sentences: Chris Brown (born 1953) is an American composer, pianist and electronic musician, who creates music for acoustic instruments with interactive electronics, for computer networks, and for improvising ensembles.
In 1986 he co-founded the pioneering computer network music ensemble "The Hub".
His 1992 electroacoustic work "Lava", for brass, percussion, and electronics is produced by Tzadik Records.
